meta.description: CLI tool to check a server's TLS/SSL capabilities

license.fullName: GNU General Public License v2.0 only

meta.long_description:
CLI tool which checks a server's service on any port for the support of
TLS/SSL ciphers, protocols as well as recent cryptographic flaws and more.
meta.name: testssl.sh
